gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 113, Celtics 96
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Celtics, 113-96, as they won their sixth consecutive game. Moritz Wagner led the Magic with a season-high 27 points (9-13 FG) as Paolo Banchero totaled 23 points, eight rebounds, and five assists. Jayson Tatum led Boston with 26 points, five rebounds, and three assists while Jaylen Brown added 18 points. The Magic improve to 11-5 in the regular season and 3-1 in East C play as the Celtics move to 12-4 and 2-1 in East C play.
